| Improvement                    | Benefit                                 |
| ------------------------------ | --------------------------------------- |
| Used `trim()`                  | Avoids empty task additions             |
| Modular `addTask()` function   | Easier to maintain or extend            |
| Removed inline `onclick`       | Better separation of logic and markup   |
| Enter key support added        | Better UX                               |
| Optional debounce can be added | Prevents rapid spam input in large apps |
